title: Health Services
content: Health Services prepares students for medical careers such as nursing, EMT, and medical assisting. Topics include anatomy and patient care.

title: Fashion and Design
content: Fashion design includes clothing construction, textiles, and fashion marketing. Careers include fashion designers and merchandisers.

title: Digital Media
content: Graphic design includes digital illustration, branding, and video production. Careers include graphic designers and video editors.

content: Agriculture education covers crop production, animal science, and environmental conservation. Careers include farming and forestry.

title: Law & Public Safety
content: This program prepares students for careers in law enforcement, firefighting, and emergency management.

title: Robotics & Engineering

title: About Us
content: Welcome to the Moanalua High School CTE Department website! This website as a project for the advanced computer science students in order to demonstrate the different pathways, people, and details of the CTE department. The courses offered in CTE are a place where students can learn about different career pathways and gain valuable skills that will help them in their future careers. The CTE department offers a variety of courses in different fields, including culinary arts, business, and technology, healthcare, and many more. a ab abo abou about about u us A Ab Abo Abou About U Us
